{"tid":1908074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[估國家] 武漢肺炎疫區信徒維持奶閘門傳統","createTime":"2020-03-03T04:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T04:50:53.000Z","uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e174a725ff4978eb826b6608b5d3737b389e13d7","tid":1908074,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"伊朗政府抗疫不力受盡批評，官員只呼籲民眾勿前往聖城兼疫區庫姆（Qom），而不關閉區內有上百萬名什葉派教徒朝拜的清真寺。民眾亦不顧衞生部呼籲，仍按傳統朝聖時親吻或觸摸聖地建築物，社交網有短片顯示，信眾在庫姆清真寺法蒂瑪聖陵（The shrine of Hazrat Masumeh）說自己「不擔心會發生甚麼事」，之後起勁地舔聖地的一道閘門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；有人要求民眾「停止用疫情嚇其他人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，甚至讚揚一名在舔門的兒童<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【武漢肺炎】加國研究估算伊朗有1.8萬宗病例 民眾疫區朝聖狂舔閘門</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200302/HBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE/?fbclid=IwAR1YZdJhNu-2iyGcD0wMAYU8rtnvy8BdXeDM4_t2YqTcypa0mFJBP4v92_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200302%2FHBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1YZdJhNu-2iyGcD0wMAYU8rtnvy8BdXeDM4_t2YqTcypa0mFJBP4v92_c&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=500be736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200302%2FHBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1YZdJhNu-2iyGcD0wMAYU8rtnvy8BdXeDM4_t2YqTcypa0mFJBP4v92_c&h=a8db6fd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200302/HBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE/?fbclid=IwAR1YZdJhNu-2iyGcD0wMAYU8rtnvy8BdXeDM4_t2YqTcypa0mFJBP4v92_c</a></span>"},{"pid":"3d5ef98080ede6c47ebe49c9b947c59187b94074","tid":1908074,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:36:10.000Z","msg":"link入面有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"